heading: 2. The 20th day of October 2022 is appointed as the day on which section
text_raw:
2. The 20th day of October 2022 is appointed as the day on which section 
22 of the Planning and Development, Maritime and Valuation (Amendment) 
Act 2022 (No. 29 of 2022) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

19 October, 2022. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 21st October, 2022.
